name: The Lane
description:
It is a story of a boy who grew up in a rural area; 
dreaming to go overseas and made a good living there. 
Many years later, he eventually made it to Japan, 
got an occupation and lots of friends there. 
However, whenever he walked by 思い出 横丁 (Memory Lane), 
he couldn't stop dreaming of going back to his hometown, 
place where he actually belongs. 

There's always two sides in everything.
